summary: This Mod Adds A Treasure Room To The Blue Palace In Solitude.
descriptionHtml:
The Blue Palace Treasure Room

This Mod Adds A Treasure Room To The Blue Palace In Solitude.
It Stores Very Valuable Items.
The Entrance Is Locked Behind A Door With Bars On The Ground Floor.
Someone Has The Key, But Who?
This Is For Master Thieves.
Try To Find The Person With The Key And Loot It From Him/Her.
Happy Hunting!

Note: This Mod Requires The Dragonborn DLC.

Instalation: Place In Skyrim Data Folder.
author: JP0005
